latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Modern minimalism, mixed touches of elegance and ethereal decor - the theme for the beautiful launch event of @interfloraindia in Ahmedabad. 

I was delighted to host the wonderful brand team in the city with the Co-Founder of @Interflora India, Anuja Joshi (@anujalunkadjoshi ) and Chirag Dengra, (@chiragdengra ) the Vice President of the brand as they interacted with the beautiful ladies of A’town and conducted a super fun Floral Workshop along with a stunning display of Interflora’s floral offerings and their fabulous gifting range! 

The brand which is synonymous with the best of floral decor for Bollywood weddings and the super fancy parties in B-Town,  has now exclusively launched their base in Ahmedabad and is available for same day deliveries (within 2hrs) via their online platform and aim to be a part of some of the most happening weddings in Gujarat. 

The event by team @toseventsandbrands was a stellar hit, as we invited a bunch of the most creative and entrepreneurial ladies and had an unforgettable evening with the perfect ambience and brilliant hi-tea set up by @seven_ahmedabad and @sujitmehta9 . 

A special thanks to @credai.gujarat.womenswing for gracing us with their presence and to @meghnamumbai for making us a part of this launch.

So proud to have gotten the opportunity to launch an iconic and the most renowned brand - Vadilal Ice Cream’s first dessert cafe: @vadilalnowforever ! Team @theopenslateofficial_ is super elated to be the Digital Media Strategists and Event Advisors, for Vadilal Now ForEver. 

A big thank you to Aakanksha Gandhi (@aashu2697 ), the Brand Director and team Now ForEver, for trusting us to be a part of their journey. 

A special thanks to @nirajsha , for creating such a stunning space and always pushing us to do good work. 

Sharing a glimpse of the launch event we hosted for the brand, which was executed in two phases. The first one with the food bloggers in the city, who always support us to make these experiences better and undoubtedly create some fantastic content for their audience to get a sneak peek of the brands offerings. The second event activity was hosted with the influencers in the city!

latestPosts.caption:
Still processing. Still obsessed.
TOKYO, YOU HAVE MY HEART!❤️ 

Tokyo isn’t just a city.. it’s a mood board!
One moment you’re sipping matcha by a centuries old temple and the next, you’re vintage shopping in Harajuku or wandering through Akihabara’s buzzing tech madness!! It’s neon and nostalgic, chaotic and calm..all at once.

You don’t just see Tokyo. You absorb it.
And one trip? Is def not enoughh! 

Drop a 🗼 if Tokyo’s on your bucket list or tell me your favourite find if you’ve already been!

latestPosts.caption:
When you’re put in charge of the trip and your mom has one dream: Mount Fuji in all its glory… and of course, it pours! 😭

But that’s what I love about travel—you stumble upon the best people. We met Ahmed, our wonderful guide, who made it his mission to help mom see Fuji. He kept tracking live views from all around the mountain and finally landed us at Lake Saiko. Boom—there she was. Fuji in full drama!
Mom lit up. Totally worth it. 😜

We picnicked with that insane view, detoured to Hakone for lavender ice cream (yes it’s a thing), devoured the Hakone cheesecake (unreal) and picked up the cutest souvenirs.

This wasn’t just sightseeing.
It was sharing her dream.
Big love to Ahmed for making it happen.
Fuji, you were something else. 🗻🫶

latestPosts.caption:
Some places feel familiar before you even get there- like they’ve been waiting for you.

Japan wasn’t part of the plan but it somehow made its way into my heart long before the flight was booked. Mom’s dream, cherry blossoms in full bloom, and this quiet magic that made me feel like I belonged. It’s not just about how beautiful everything is (though wow, it really is) — it’s how Japan feels. Like a gentle nudge saying, “stay a little longer.”

Still wrapping my head around how a place can feel like home and a memory all at once.

latestPosts.caption:
Not all experiences are created equal—and The Gathering (@thegatheringindia ) proved just that. Set against the stunning backdrop of Travancore Palace (@travancorepalace.newdelhi ), this wasn’t just an event—it was immersive dining at its finest. Think 9 chefs, 9 artists, and 9 distinct pop up restaurants - each telling a story through flavors, visuals, and pure sensory magic. Every course felt like stepping into a new narrative, blending gastronomy with visual and sensory storytelling in the most unexpected ways.

My top pick? The Boring Dinner by Gresham Fernandes (@greshamfernandes )—and trust me, boring was not on the menu. It was all about contrast and dualities, with futuristic bites straight out of 2079. AI inspired food, future forward concepts,  and flavors that had me questioning whether I was still in 2025.

Pulling off restaurant pop ups is no easy feat. Crafting these immersive spaces from concept to execution, is a whole production in itself. But here..every detail was on point. While the food was undoubtedly the star, the experience design brought it all together—sparking connection, celebrating creativity, and turning every meal into a shared story. Already counting down to the next edition—because once you’ve dined in the future, the present just doesn’t taste the same.

#TheGathering #ImmersiveDining #CulinaryArt #FutureOnAPlate #SensoryStorytelling #ContrastAndDualities

Kai Po Che: A Celebration to Remember! 🪁🍾

Just a week ago, TOS Experiences launched with the most anticipated event in the stunning heritage haveli and historic lanes of Old Ahmedabad, leaving us basking in its magic.

From centuries-old walls reimagined with vibrant Uttarayan themes to kites, fireworks, and soulful melodies lighting up the sky, every moment was a testament to thoughtful craftsmanship.

More than just the sights and sounds, it was the laughter, connections, and shared stories that made the night truly unforgettable.

A heartfelt thank you to our incredible guests for making this journey special and to our sponsors for their support:
✨ Experience Partner – @kensvillegolfliving 
🚘 Luxury Partner – @mercedesbenzind @grouplandmark 
🩺 Wellness Partner – @zydusuniverse 

Here’s to many more milestones together! 🪁🎆💛

#KaiPoChe #CelebrationToRemember #UttarayanVibes #TOSExperiences #AhmedabadDiaries #HeritageHaveli #OldCityMagic #VibrantIndia #unforgettablemoments

What started as a dream to create something truly special has now turned into The Open Slate Experiences (@tosexperiencesbyradhika )! With our first event ‘Kai Po Che’ kicking things off, we set out to redefine how experiences are created—not just in Ahmedabad, but beyond.

TOS Experiences; isn’t just about events-it’s about curating moments that bring people together, spark creativity and celebrate life in its most vibrant form. A big shoutout to everyone who showed up, cheered us on, and made this milestone unforgettable. 

The journey has only just begun, and trust us—it’s going to get bigger, bolder, and oh-so-cooler! 😉

P.S. Keep an eye out for what’s next (March it is)—the best is yet to come!
